# Design Guidelines - AI & Data Platform (Web3)

## Design Approach
**Reference-Based:** OpenSea-inspired marketplace with adaptations for AI dataset ecosystem. Modern Web3 marketplace aesthetic with clean, professional interface optimized for browsing collections, detailed item views, and transaction flows.

## Core Design Principles
1. **Marketplace Focus:** Card-based browsing with rich previews and metadata
2. **Web3 Native:** Blockchain transaction states, wallet integration, on-chain verification indicators
3. **Data-Centric:** Emphasize dataset quality, contributor reputation, and transparent royalty splits
4. **Professional Trust:** Clean, credible design for enterprise AI/ML builders

## Typography
- **Primary Font:** Inter (Google Fonts) - clean, modern sans-serif
- **Hierarchy:**
  - H1: 2.5rem (40px), font-bold - Hero headlines, page titles
  - H2: 2rem (32px), font-semibold - Section headers
  - H3: 1.5rem (24px), font-semibold - Card titles, subsections
  - Body: 1rem (16px), font-normal - Primary content
  - Small: 0.875rem (14px), font-normal - Metadata, labels
  - Tiny: 0.75rem (12px), font-medium - Badges, timestamps

## Layout System
- **Spacing Scale:** Tailwind units 2, 4, 6, 8, 12, 16, 24 (p-2, m-4, gap-6, py-8, etc.)
- **Container:** max-w-7xl for main content
- **Grid Systems:**
  - Cards: grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4
  - Stats: grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4
  - Details: lg:grid-cols-3 (2/3 main content, 1/3 sidebar)

## Navigation Structure

### Sidebar Navigation (Persistent, Left-aligned)
- Logo at top with deep purple accent
- Main sections with icons:
  - Discover (Home icon)
  - Projects (Folder icon)
  - Marketplace (Shopping bag icon)
  - Activity (Clock icon)
  - Leaderboards (Trophy icon)
- Authenticated sections (below divider):
  - Dashboard, Create Project, My Projects, My Submissions, My Datasets, Earnings
- Footer: Network status indicator, Help link
- Width: 240px desktop, collapsible on tablet/mobile to icon-only (64px) or drawer

### Top Navbar
- Search bar (center-aligned, expandable, with filters dropdown)
- Right side: Activity bell icon (with badge), Connect Wallet button (deep purple, rounded-lg), Profile avatar dropdown
- Sticky on scroll with subtle shadow

## Component Library

### Cards (Project/Dataset)
- Rounded-xl borders with subtle shadow
- Hover: lift effect (translate-y-1 + shadow-lg)
- Structure:
  - Image/Preview (aspect-video or aspect-square)
  - Badge overlay (status: Open/Closed/Completed in top-left)
  - Content padding: p-4
  - Title (font-semibold, text-lg)
  - Metadata row: icons + text (submissions count, reward amount, deadline)
  - Footer: Creator avatar + name, Action button/link

### Buttons
- Primary: Deep purple (#6B46C1) background, white text, rounded-lg, px-6 py-3
- Secondary: Purple-100 background, purple-700 text, rounded-lg
- Ghost: Transparent with purple-700 text, border-2 border-purple-300
- Icon buttons: Square, rounded-lg, hover:bg-purple-50
- Over images: Backdrop blur (backdrop-blur-md), white/10 background, white text

### Stats/Metrics
- Large number (text-3xl font-bold) above small label (text-sm text-gray-500)
- Group in grid with subtle borders or cards
- Use icons for context (trending up/down, user icons, currency)

### Badges
- Rounded-full px-3 py-1 with colored backgrounds:
  - Open: green-100 background, green-700 text
  - Closed: gray-100 background, gray-700 text
  - Verified: purple-100 background, purple-700 text
- Font-medium text-xs

### Forms
- Input fields: border-gray-300, rounded-lg, px-4 py-3, focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500
- Labels: font-medium text-sm mb-2
- File uploads: Dashed border drag-drop areas with icon and helper text
- Form sections: Space with mb-8, use dividers (border-t pt-8)

### Modals/Overlays
- Backdrop: bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm
- Content: bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-2xl p-8
- Close button: top-right, rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100

### Data Tables
- Header: bg-gray-50, font-semibold, text-sm
- Rows: border-b hover:bg-gray-50
- Cells: px-6 py-4
- Actions column: Icon buttons aligned right

## Page-Specific Layouts

### Home/Discover
- Hero: Large search bar, headline, CTA (Create Project + Browse Marketplace buttons)
- Featured Projects: Horizontal scrollable cards (4-5 visible)
- Featured Datasets: Grid layout (4 columns)
- Leaderboards: Two columns (Contributors left, Curators right)
- Stats banner: 4-column metrics
- Activity feed: Single column, max-w-3xl centered

### Projects Browse & Marketplace
- Filters sidebar (left, collapsible): Categories, price range, status, sort options
- Results area: Grid with view toggle (grid/list) in top-right
- Pagination at bottom

### Detail Pages (Project/Dataset)
- Three-column layout:
  - Left (2/3): Image gallery, description, stats, activity
  - Right (1/3 sticky): Purchase/Submit card, metadata, creator info
- Tabs for additional sections: About, Contributors, Activity, Related

### Dashboard
- Widget grid: 4-column on desktop, stack on mobile
- Quick actions: Large icon buttons in 2x2 or 3-column grid
- Recent activity list below

## Images
- **Logo:** Use logo.png (deep purple V with network graphic) in sidebar top and footer
- **Hero Section (Home):** Abstract data visualization or network nodes graphic (purple/blue gradient), full-width, height: 60vh
- **Project/Dataset Cards:** Thumbnail images (640x480 placeholder) showing data samples or project icons
- **Profile Avatars:** Circular, 40x40px in cards, 80x80px in profiles
- **Empty States:** Illustration of data collection/AI training process with purple accents

## Color Palette
Primary: Deep Purple (#6B46C1 / purple-600) from logo
Supporting: purple-50 through purple-900 scale
Neutrals: gray-50 through gray-900
Success: green-500, Warning: yellow-500, Error: red-500

## Responsive Behavior
- Mobile (<768px): Sidebar collapses to drawer, cards single column, simplified stats
- Tablet (768-1024px): Sidebar icon-only, cards 2-column, condensed navigation
- Desktop (>1024px): Full sidebar, multi-column grids, expanded metadata